cat.lump.aq.textextraction.wikipedia.cli

Class WikipediaCliMinimum

  • java.lang.Object
    • cat.lump.aq.textextraction.wikipedia.cli.WikipediaCliMinimum
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LuceneCliCategoriesXecutor, LuceneCliIndexerWPar, LuceneCliQuerierWPar, LuceneCliWPar2Query, WikipediaCliArticleSelector, WikipediaCliArticleTextExtractor, WikipediaCliCategoriesXecutor, WikipediaCliCategoryDepth, WikipediaCliCategoryExtractor, WikipediaCliDomainKeywords, WikipediaCliFragmentsXecutor

    public abstract class WikipediaCliMinimum
extends java.lang.Object
    CLI to access JWPL-WIKIPEDIA-related programs in this package. This class contains the minimum parameters required to setup a JWPL instance of Wikipedia, namely language and year, and to initialise the WikiTailor and IR-based methods for in-domain corpora extraction.
    Author:
    albarron, cristina
